@startuml 04-ssd-perception-pipeline
!include _style.iuml

title <b>Perception Pipeline — apriltag_docking</b>\n<size:18><color:#5D6D7E>Zero-copy composable container · tag36h11 · 10 Hz</color></size>

left to right direction

component "RPi Camera V2" as CamHW <<io>>

package "apriltag_vision_container\n<size:14><color:#5D6D7E>single-process, use_intra_process_comms=true</color></size>" as Container {
  component "camera_ros::CameraNode\n<size:14>1640×1232 · BGR888 · 10 Hz</size>"   as CamNode <<io>>
  component "image_proc::ResizeNode\n<size:14>640×480 · nearest-neighbor</size>"   as Resize
  component "image_proc::RectifyNode\n<size:14>undistort · nearest</size>"         as Rectify
  component "apriltag_ros::AprilTagNode\n<size:14>tag36h11 · size 0.0986 m</size>" as Tag
}

component "detected_dock_pose_publisher_0\n<size:14>child: nav2_dock_target_0</size>" as Pub0
component "detected_dock_pose_publisher_2\n<size:14>child: nav2_dock_target_2</size>" as Pub2

component "docker.py\n<size:14>(Laptop)</size>" as Docker <<coord>>

CamHW   --> CamNode : <size:14>CSI raw</size>

CamNode -right-> Resize  : <size:14>/camera/image_raw</size>\n<size:14>+ /camera/camera_info</size>
Resize  -right-> Rectify : <size:14>/camera/resized/image_raw</size>\n<size:14>+ /camera/resized/camera_info</size>
Rectify -right-> Tag     : <size:14>/camera/resized/image_rect</size>

Tag --> Pub0 : <size:14>TF camera → tag36h11:0</size>
Tag --> Pub2 : <size:14>TF camera → tag36h11:2</size>

Pub0 --> Docker : <size:14>/detected_dock_pose_0</size>\n<size:14>PoseStamped @ 10 Hz</size>
Pub2 --> Docker : <size:14>/detected_dock_pose_2</size>\n<size:14>PoseStamped @ 10 Hz</size>

Tag  ..> Docker : <size:14>/detections</size>\n<size:14>AprilTagDetectionArray</size>

@enduml
